name: Spurs
summary: Following a standout performance from Victor Wembanyama, who scored 42 points against the Spurs, the San Antonio franchise has become a potential destination for NBA trades. The Spurs, who are fielding trade calls, have emerged as contenders for top players like De'Aaron Fox. Wembanyama's impressive display has sparked excitement among NBA fans, making the Spurs a team to watch. In recent games, the Spurs faced the Atlanta Hawks in an overtime thriller, ultimately winning 133-126. They are preparing to face the Philadelphia 76ers and have hinted at potential roster changes. The team's upcoming Christmas game against the New York Knicks will feature animated characters, adding to the festive spirit. Additionally, fans can follow the Spurs' matchup against the Hawks and their upcoming game against the 76ers through various live streaming and TV broadcast options.

name: Crocodile Dundee
summary: Burt, the iconic saltwater crocodile who gained fame for his cameo in the "Crocodile Dundee" movie, has passed away at an estimated age of over 90 years. The beloved reptile, renowned for its hot-tempered demeanor, resided in a reptile habitat in Australia and was a star attraction. His demise marks the end of an era for both animal enthusiasts and those who cherish the legacy of "Crocodile Dundee."

name: Knicks
summary: The New York Knicks are riding high, as evidenced by their recent successes against the Minnesota Timberwolves and their rise in the NBA power rankings. Led by star center Karl-Anthony Towns, who had a standout performance in a revenge game against his former team, the Knicks have also benefited from the acquisition of Mikal Bridges, who has emerged as a formidable trash-talker. The team's commitment to fielding their best players, even during back-to-back games, has fostered valuable cohesion and helped them establish themselves as a competitive force. The Knicks have also made a savvy move by bringing back experienced guard Shamet, adding depth to their roster. Their upcoming matchup against the Toronto Raptors on December 23rd promises to be another exciting test as they continue to ascend in the NBA standings.

name: NORAD Santa tracker
summary: NORAD's Santa tracker, which began as a Cold War morale booster, has evolved into a popular tradition, drawing millions of children annually. Various organizations, including Statesman Journal, TechRadar, Yahoo Life, and CBS News, provide information on how to track Santa's journey on Christmas Eve using NORAD's interactive tracker. This tracker allows individuals to follow Santa's progress around the globe, see his reindeer, and even access the tracker in different languages. The creation of this tracker stemmed from a wrong number call to a military phone, which has resulted in countless fans worldwide and become a cherished holiday tradition, bringing joy and excitement to children during the festive season.

name: Nordstrom family
summary: The Nordstrom family is regaining control of the department store chain Nordstrom in a $6.25 billion deal. The family is partnering with Mexican company El Puerto de Liverpool to take the company private. The Nordstrom family has a long history with the company, which was founded by their great-grandfather in 1901. The family has been gradually increasing its stake in the company in recent years, and this deal will give them complete ownership. The deal is expected to close in the second half of 2023, and Nordstrom will no longer be publicly traded.
